cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR 

The paper deals with computer vision and deep learning techniques for detecting and classifying GAN-generated images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories as well. Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia data, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category. Finally, the paper also deals with the security implications of GAN-generated images, which makes cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category.
